So, uh... what we're gonna do</i>

00:30.965 --> 00:33.067
is we're gonna play back
some of the band's new songs.

00:33.234 --> 00:35.803
There'll be no cameras
allowed in there.

00:35.970 --> 00:36.937
There'll be no video,

00:37.104 --> 00:38.406
no bags in there.

00:38.572 --> 00:40.441
You can only walk in
with paper and a pencil.

00:40.608 --> 00:41.809
<i>MAN".
We're ready.</i>

00:41.976 --> 00:42.977
<i>WOMAN:
Okay. Go ahead.</i>

00:43.144 --> 00:45.079
<i>HARMON:
Are there any questions?</i>

00:45.246 --> 00:46.213
WOMAN:
Okay.

00:47.515 --> 00:50.084
