<i>HAMMETT: Maybe we should talk
about next week.</i>

28:29.241 --> 28:31.277
Well, all next
week is therapy.

28:31.444 --> 28:32.411
Yeah.

28:32.578 --> 28:34.747
HETFIELD:
Do we have to do that?

28:34.914 --> 28:36.882
Can we sack Phil?

28:37.983 --> 28:39.618
ULRICH:
I mean...

28:39.785 --> 28:41.654
we gotta find...

28:41.821 --> 28:43.622
we gotta find
a balance to not...

28:43.789 --> 28:45.057
you know,
the Phil stuffs important,

