and I hope we all feel

28:46.192 --> 28:47.927
that that's an investment

28:48.094 --> 28:50.763
in the music.

28:50.930 --> 28:52.631
It's an important
part of the record.

28:52.798 --> 28:54.567
<i>II'</i>

28:59.505 --> 29:03.275
♪ Get all holy again ♪

