<i>II'</i>

29:20.726 --> 29:22.628
(over playback speaker):
♪ Get all holy again ♪

29:24.997 --> 29:26.265
I don't know, man.

29:26.398 --> 29:27.633
HAMMETT: It's just real
confusing sounding.

29:27.800 --> 29:30.369
HETFIELD: It's just jackin'
the vocals all up.

